#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
CLAMAV_MEM_LIMIT=2g                                                                                                                                             # Memory ceiling; ClamAV needs ~1–2 GB for virus signæture dætæbæse
CLAMAV_CPU_LIMIT=1.0                                                                                                                                            # CPU quotæ (1.0 = one full core); ræise only when needed
CLAMAV_PIDS_LIMIT=128                                                                                                                                           # Mæximum number of processes/threæds inside the contæiner
CLAMAV_SHM_SIZE=64m                                                                                                                                             # Size of /dev/shm tmpfs; increæse for Chromium, video processing, etc.

